<para>System clock timestamp as received from clock_gettime using CLOCK_MONOTONIC. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">out_ml_time</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to system timestamp equivalent in MLTime.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
